  "title": "Part Time - Retail Associates (Luxury Fashion - Airport)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver outstanding customer service and sales assistance to all customers</p></li><li><p>Maintain store presentation and visual merchandising standards</p></li><li><p>Process sales transactions accurately and efficiently</p></li><li><p>Assist in managing stock levels and replenishment</p></li><li><p>Contribute to the achievement of sales targets and key performance indicators</p></li><li><p>Identifies and handles customers’ inquiries and concerns in accordance to company and airport (refund) policy</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior experience in luxury fashion retail or in similar capacity</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills to engage with a diverse customer base</p></li><li><p>Excellent product knowledge and the ability to make informed recommendations</p></li><li><p>Attention to detail and a passion for maintaining high standards of presentation</p></li><li><p>Comfortable to working in Changi Airport on retail shift hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p>A positive, service-oriented attitude and the ability to work collaboratively in a team</p></li></ul>",
